About Me
My name’s Fahim. I’m an incoming University of Waterloo student, passionate about computer science and finance.
About the Project
My project, The Title of My Project, contains a graph that shows the negative correlation between a car’s fuel efficiency and weight.
Goals
I learn through this project.
I’m proud of this project.
I will add multiple graphs.

“This is data science” ~ Preceptor
